OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny daytime
OL,6,Fshowers slowly easing to leave a
OL,7,Flargely dry night, with clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping for many. Turning locally
OL,9,Fchilly, especially in some prone rural
OL,10,Fspots. Cloud building from the west
OL,11,Flater in the night. Winds mostly light
OL,12,Fthroughout.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fwill spread eastwards across all parts
OL,16,Fduring the morning. Rain will be
OL,17,Flocally heavy, especially on western
OL,18,Fhills. Windy, locally gusty on hills.
OL,19,FFeeling humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
