OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and brighter spells, with some
OL,7,Fscattered light showers on Friday,
OL,8,Fthese easing later. Breezy. Dry with
OL,9,Fsunny spells on Saturday and Sunday.
OL,10,FFeeling warmer, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
